The code was written in PHP 5.5.4 on Apache httpd

This is the tree which you have to copy to a PHP enabled webserver directory.

Note that you best include "include/root.php" when you start new directories.
Also, have a look at "include/include.std.php"

php.portal (aka phpHackerPortal)
================================

PHP code for a portal site for hackers

Load index.example.html for the program listing. 
